<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7882> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7882" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Aed. pl. , Dated to 83, with a query, in MRR 2.63, 65, note 4. See now Crawford, RRC 1.367, no. 351, 86 B.C. See below on M. Fannius (15).\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7246> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7246" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Aed. pl. 86, pr. 80. In MRR 2.63, and Index, 565, transfer the notices of L. Fan(nius) and L. Crit(onius), aediles of the plebs, from 83 to 86 (to MRR 2.54), and refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.367, no. 151. The date in 86 makes uncertain the date of his subsequent service as iudex quaestionis (MRR 2.76) when he presided over the quaestio de sicariis et veneficis (Cic. Rosc. Amer. 11), perhaps as early as 85, before presiding over it again as praetor in 80. See T. E. Kinsey, Mnemosyne 20, 1967, 61-67.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4233> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4233" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Cic. Rosc. Amer. 11-12; Schol, Gron. 304 Stangl." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4205> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4205" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "A Iudex in the Quaestio de sicariis before he presided over the same court as Praetor in 80 (Cic. Rosc. Amer. 11)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4115> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4115" ;
